data.description: Spacious pool home with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bath home in Sherwood at the Crossroads. Warranty remediation has just been completed by Beazer Homes which included new tile flooring and tile walls in bathrooms, new laminate flooring and new carpet. Brand new matching stainless steel Whirlpool appliances in kitchen. All 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and laundry room are located on the second level. Crown molding throughout. Large screened and partially covered patio with heated pool. Exceptional master suite with large soaking tub, separate walk in shower with new floor to ceiling tile, dual sinks and his and hers walk-in closets. Conveniently located close to Fort Myers and I-75. Low HOA fees, just $75 per month.
